                                Command : TURN

NAME
   turn - Turn game on or off, or change the login message

Level: Expert

SYNTAX
   [##:##] Command : turn <on|off|motd>

"turn  off"  turns  the game off: mortal players can't log in, and mortals al-
ready logged will be booted at the next command prompt.  The command lets  you
enter  a message to the players explaining the downtime.  Updates are not dis-
abled.

"turn on" reverts the effect of "turn off".

"turn motd" lets you enter a new login message, also known  as  motto  of  the
day.

SEE ALSO
   Deity

